title: Ikar Tosafot Yom Tov on Mishnah Bekhorot
enDesc: Ikar Tosafot Yom Yov is an abridged version of Rabbi Yom Tov Lippmann Heller’s 1579 - 1654) classic commentary on the Mishnah - Tosafot Yom Tov. The author’s objective for writing his commentary was to add to and compliment the Bartenura.
